  <title>Plane</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Definition<keyword>Plane</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Planes</text> are coincident with their <text styleclass="VariableName-small">XY-axes</text> of their <text styleclass="VariableName-small">XYZ Coordinate-System</text>.</para>
          <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">You can add <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Planes</text> and <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editors</text> to <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Planes</text>.</li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">The <text styleclass="VariableName-small">XY-axes</text> of a new <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Plane</text> and a <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editor</text> are coincident with those of its parent <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Plane</text>. </li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">The <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Front-View</text> of a <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editor</text> is normal to the <text styleclass="Popup Box2">XY-axes </text>of the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Plane</text>.</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Model-AddPlane">Model | Add Plane</link></para>
